HEADWORD: Griffe
<hw>Griffe</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The offspring of a mulatto woman and a negro; also, a
mulatto.</def> <mark>[Local, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A person of mixed negro and American Indian
blood.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Griffin</ent>⟦br⟧
